<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="A layout example with a side menu that hides on mobile, just like the Pure website.">
    <title>Responsive Side Menu &ndash; Layout Examples &ndash; Pure</title>


    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/purecss@1.0.0/build/pure-min.css" integrity="sha384-" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>
<body>






<div id="layout">
    <!-- Menu toggle -->
    <a href="#menu" id="menuLink" class="menu-link">
        <!-- Hamburger icon -->
        <span></span>
    </a>


    <div id="main">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>VotingWebsite</h1>
        </div>
        <div id="menu">
            <div class="pure-menu">

                <ul class="pure-menu-list">
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Log In</a></li>
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Register</a></li>
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Survey</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">

            <h2 class="content-subhead">We all know everybody have a chance to choice, now it is the time to choice</h2>
            <p>
                Warning, in order to keep our website runing, we have to get some additional information from you. Please do a suvey before you do the survey. Sorry for the inconvenience.
            </p>

            <div class="pure-g">
                <div class="pure-u-1-4">
                    <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="http://i2.cdn.turner.com/money/dam/assets/161107113845-election2016-vote-780x439.jpg" alt="Peyto Lake">
                </div>
            </div>


        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
